observations:
=============
  * this data structure:
    - is embedded in the webpage
    - contains all available episodes

analysis of video urls for first episode in list:
=================================================
{
  var data   = JSON.parse( window.document.querySelector('script#__NEXT_DATA__').innerText )
  var videos = data.props.initialState.video.current.associatedVideoPlaylist.videos || data.props.initialState.video.associatedPlaylists[0].videos

  // filter invalid list items
  videos = videos.filter(function(video){
    return (
         (video.videoType === 'broadcast')
      && ('object' === typeof video.url)
      && ('object' === typeof video.headline)
      && ('object' === typeof video.description)
      && ('object' === typeof video.closedCaptioning)
      && (Array.isArray(video.videoAssets) && video.videoAssets.length)
    )
  })

  // preprocess list of videos
  videos = videos.map(function(video){
    return video.videoAssets
  })

  if (videos.length)
    console.log(JSON.stringify(videos[0], null, 2))
}

sample filter (all available episodes):
=======================================
{
  var data   = JSON.parse( window.document.querySelector('script#__NEXT_DATA__').innerText )
  var videos = data.props.initialState.video.current.associatedVideoPlaylist.videos || data.props.initialState.video.associatedPlaylists[0].videos

  // filter invalid list items
  videos = videos.filter(function(video){
    return (
         (video.videoType === 'broadcast')
      && ('object' === typeof video.url)
      && ('object' === typeof video.headline)
      && ('object' === typeof video.description)
      && ('object' === typeof video.closedCaptioning)
      && (Array.isArray(video.videoAssets) && video.videoAssets.length)
    )
  })

  // preprocess list of videos
  videos = videos.map(function(video){
    var videoAsset = video.videoAssets.find(function(asset){
      return (
           (asset.assetType === 'EMP')
        && (asset.format === 'M3U')
        && (asset.publicUrl)
      )
    })

    return (!videoAsset)
      ? null
      : {
        url:         video.url.canonical,
        title:       video.headline.primary,
        description: video.description.primary,
        videos:      {
          hls:       videoAsset.publicUrl + '#video.m3u8'
        },
        duration:    videoAsset.assetDuration * 1000,
        date:        (new Date(video.datePublished)).toLocaleDateString(),
        caption_url: video.closedCaptioning.webvtt || video.closedCaptioning.srt || video.closedCaptioning.smptett || ''
      }
  })

  console.log(videos.length)
  console.log(JSON.stringify(videos, null, 2))
}

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

sample filter (current episode only):
=====================================
{
  var data   = JSON.parse( window.document.querySelector('script#__NEXT_DATA__').innerText )
  var videos = [data.props.initialState.video.current]

  // filter invalid list items
  videos = videos.filter(function(video){
    return (
         (video.videoType === 'broadcast')
      && ('object' === typeof video.url)
      && ('object' === typeof video.headline)
      && ('object' === typeof video.description)
      && ('object' === typeof video.closedCaptioning)
      && (Array.isArray(video.videoAssets) && video.videoAssets.length)
    )
  })

  // preprocess list of videos
  videos = videos.map(function(video){
    var videoAsset = video.videoAssets.find(function(asset){
      return (
           (asset.assetType === 'EMP')
        && (asset.format === 'M3U')
        && (asset.publicUrl)
      )
    })

    return (!videoAsset)
      ? null
      : {
        url:         video.url.canonical,
        title:       video.headline.primary,
        description: video.description.primary,
        videos:      {
          hls:       videoAsset.publicUrl + '#video.m3u8'
        },
        duration:    videoAsset.assetDuration * 1000,
        date:        (new Date(video.datePublished)).toLocaleDateString(),
        caption_url: video.closedCaptioning.webvtt || video.closedCaptioning.srt || video.closedCaptioning.smptett || ''
      }
  })

  console.log(videos.length)
  console.log(JSON.stringify(videos, null, 2))
}

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

compatability (update):
=======================
  * ExoPlayer:
    - redirect from HTTP to HTTPS fails
    - solution is to update the HTTP URL (before redirect) to HTTPS,
      so redirect from HTTPS to HTTPS succeeds
    - example:
      * original HTTP URL:
          http://link.theplatform.com/s/rksNhC/flXCcqIAaspE#video.m3u8
      * updated HTTPS URL:
          https://link.theplatform.com/s/rksNhC/flXCcqIAaspE#video.m3u8

----------------------------------------

curl -I "https://link.theplatform.com/s/rksNhC/flXCcqIAaspE"
  HTTP/1.1 302 Found
  Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *
  Location: https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/mtp_netcast_230219/1/index.m3u8
